simergy.core.patients

Class Patient

  • java.lang.Object
    • simergy.core.patients.Patient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Patient
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class Patient. This class is used to represent a patient in the ED. Attributes name, and surname are not mandatory. Contains all the personal informations about a patient.
    See Also:
    to get informations about patient's stay in the ed., Serialized Form
